'''''Animals Are Beautiful People''''' <ref>https://moviesanywhere.com/movie/animals-are-beautiful-people</ref> (nanone yitwa '''''Beautiful People''''') ni documentaire y’ibidukikije yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo yo mu 1974 yanditswe<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/animals_are_beautiful_people</ref>, yakozwe, iyoborwa, ifatwa amashusho kandi ihindurwa na Jamie Uys<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/1985/08/02/movies/the-screen-animals-are-beautiful-people.html</ref>, ivuga ku nyamaswa zo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika yepfo]], zerekanwe nibintu bisetsa<ref>http://decentfilms.com/reviews/animalsarebeautifulpeople</ref>. Yafatiwe amashusho mu butayu bwa Namib, ubutayu bwa Kalahari n'umugezi wa Okavango na Delta ya Okavango<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/figure/Animals-Are-Beautiful-People-1974-directed-by-Jamie-Uys_fig5_254941459</ref> .. yahawe igihembo cya Golden Globe 1974 muri Filime Nziza<ref>https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/animals-are-beautiful-people/8d6kgwzl5jbs</ref> .Iyi filime, intsinzi ikomeye mu bucuruzi, yakozwe mu bwigenge na Uys, izwi kandi nyuma yo gusetsa  muri  ''[[The Gods Must Be Crazy]]'' (1980).<ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/animals-are-beautiful-people/oclc/52297633</ref> 

== Umuziki wa kera ==
